Leonora von Ottinger https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leonora_von_Ottinger 0 Leonora von Ottinger was an American silent film and stage actress. She only starred in 16 films in total and concentrated on stage acting. She starred alongside William Garwood in a number of short films. Her spouse was Benjamin Von Ottinger of Larchmont New York.
